        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2023-11-06T12:10:52.8729291Z",
          "locale_text": "« Les Drukharis sont vraiment venus ici ? Pourquoi ? »",
          "speaker": "",
          "speaker_gender": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "esES",
      "text": "«¿Los Drukhari han venido a este mundo? ¿Por qué?».",
      "modification_date": "2024-02-26T17:29:03.2157772Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2024-02-26T17:29:03.2157774Z",
      "original_text": "\"The Drukhari have come to this world? Why?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2023-09-12T08:36:00.9522211Z",
          "locale_text": "«¿Aquí han estado los Drukhari? ¿Por qué?».",
          "speaker": "",
          "speaker_gender": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“黑暗灵族来过这个世界？他们来这里干什么？”",
      "modification_date": "2024-03-25T13:52:22.1205908Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2024-03-25T13:52:22.1205914Z",
      "original_text": "\"The Drukhari have come to this world? Why?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2023-09-20T12:03:39.6764779Z",
          "locale_text": "“这里之前真的有黑暗灵族吗？他们来这里干什么？”",
          "speaker": "",
          "speaker_gender": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "jaJP",
      "text": "「デュカーリがこの世界に来ていただと？何故だ？」",
